name: My Latest Sales
description:
What?
- This experimental NFT can be used to quickly see your latest sales on h=n. 

How?
- Just open the NFT. 

Requirements?
- You need to sync your wallet on the platform where you are watching the NFT.

Why?
- Just to see if you sold anything :)

No guarantees that this NFT will be working. The NFT is using the hicdex GraphQL API which can be removed or restricted at any time (or it just don't works sometimes). Collect it only for fun.
